WEBVTT

00:00:07.610 --> 00:00:14.490
<font face="Times New Roman" size="30"><b>The Apothecary <font color="#000000">Diaries</font></b></font>

00:01:28.270 --> 00:01:29.980
<font face="Times New Roman" size="30"><b>{\an3}<font size="24">The Apothecary <font color="#000000">Diaries</font></font></b></font>

00:01:30.440 --> 00:01:33.440
<font size="10">{\an1}This story is a work of fiction. The names of all of the characters, organizations, and so on
 are imaginary. It also bears no connection to any specific real-life events.</font>

00:01:42.170 --> 00:01:43.460
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Excuse me.</font>

00:01:43.460 --> 00:01:44.540
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Master Jinshi.</font>

00:01:45.100 --> 00:01:47.510
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}I heard Concubine Gyokuyou
has gone into labor.</font>

00:01:45.580 --> 00:01:49.540
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20">{\an3}Episode 42: Lantern Plant</font>

00:01:47.510 --> 00:01:49.750
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}Yes, as of this morning.</font>

00:01:49.750 --> 00:01:54.090
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">We expect the actual birth to be a little 
later, but we're getting ready anyway.</font>

00:01:54.790 --> 00:01:55.760
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">This way.</font>

00:02:06.950 --> 00:02:08.060
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">How is she?</font>

00:02:08.360 --> 00:02:10.650
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">She's stable.</font>

00:02:11.030 --> 00:02:14.720
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Her contractions have subsided, 
and she doesn't seem to be fatigued.</font>

00:02:15.690 --> 00:02:16.560
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I see.</font>

00:02:17.210 --> 00:02:20.570
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">It's still unclear when 
the actual birth will take place.</font>

00:02:21.150 --> 00:02:22.950
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">How is the baby doing?</font>

00:02:22.950 --> 00:02:26.340
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">If you're talking about the breech birth, 
that is no longer a concern.</font>

00:02:26.340 --> 00:02:29.930
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">It seems like Maomao's treatments worked.</font>

00:02:31.670 --> 00:02:32.730
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Maomao...</i></font>

00:02:34.630 --> 00:02:37.700
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>It's already been ten days 
since she went missing.</i></font>

00:02:38.490 --> 00:02:39.690
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Is she alright?</i></font>

00:02:46.860 --> 00:02:50.840
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">L-Luomen, what can I do to help?</font>

00:02:50.840 --> 00:02:52.850
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Doctor, out of the way!</font>

00:02:52.850 --> 00:02:55.460
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Don't stand in the doorway, please!</font>

00:02:56.650 --> 00:02:58.420
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Just look after the cat.</font>

00:02:58.420 --> 00:02:59.470
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yes!</font>

00:03:04.810 --> 00:03:08.870
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>It's a bit reassuring to have someone else 
more panicked than me around.</i></font>

00:03:13.470 --> 00:03:17.750
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I'll depart for now. Please let me 
know if something happens.</font>

00:03:18.900 --> 00:03:19.920
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Master Jinshi!</font>

00:03:20.390 --> 00:03:21.220
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What is it?</font>

00:03:22.740 --> 00:03:25.080
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">It's about the missing eunuch.</font>

00:03:29.190 --> 00:03:31.310
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">So, what did you find?</font>

00:03:31.900 --> 00:03:33.890
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The eunuch is named Tian.</font>

00:03:33.890 --> 00:03:36.910
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">He was supposed to be 
a slave from a foreign nation,</font>

00:03:36.910 --> 00:03:40.820
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">but none of the others who arrived 
with him were acquainted with him.</font>

00:03:40.820 --> 00:03:43.950
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">He must have snuck in somewhere.</font>

00:03:45.720 --> 00:03:47.950
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">In order to infiltrate the rear palace.</font>

00:03:49.210 --> 00:03:53.130
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">He probably kept his distance from 
the others to maintain that secret.</font>

00:03:53.130 --> 00:03:56.110
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Because of that, we barely 
have any information on him.</font>

00:03:58.310 --> 00:03:59.130
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Anything else?</font>

00:03:59.130 --> 00:04:02.390
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">He was seen praying at a shrine.</font>

00:04:02.830 --> 00:04:05.660
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">That's not strange. 
Maybe he was just religious.</font>

00:04:06.510 --> 00:04:07.850
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Well...</font>

00:04:12.860 --> 00:04:15.850
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The graveyard on the north side?</font>

00:04:15.850 --> 00:04:16.310
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yes.</font>

00:04:16.940 --> 00:04:21.940
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The graves of those who were deflowered by 
the late emperor, who died in the rear palace.</font>

00:04:25.560 --> 00:04:30.260
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Tian was seen paying his respects 
to one of the graves there.</font>

00:04:35.080 --> 00:04:39.740
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Those who were deflowered 
by the late emperor at a young age</i></font>

00:04:40.150 --> 00:04:42.940
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>were never allowed to leave 
the rear palace, even after death.</i></font>

00:04:48.090 --> 00:04:53.800
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>They vanished in this garden, without 
even a record of their names kept.</i></font>

00:05:01.910 --> 00:05:03.530
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Is that a worker from the clinic?</font>

00:05:04.940 --> 00:05:06.940
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">E-Excuse me.</font>

00:05:12.330 --> 00:05:13.580
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>This smell...</i></font>

00:05:22.050 --> 00:05:23.420
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Where did Maomao go?!</font>

00:05:29.320 --> 00:05:33.060
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Calm down! I'm "Jinshi the Eunuch" right now.</i></font>

00:05:33.060 --> 00:05:34.560
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>I have to be my usual self...</i></font>

00:05:37.980 --> 00:05:39.960
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I'm looking for the freckled lady-in-waiting,</font>

00:05:39.960 --> 00:05:42.580
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">the one working for the Jade Pavilion.</font>

00:05:43.060 --> 00:05:44.750
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Do you know who I'm talking about?</font>

00:05:54.690 --> 00:05:56.040
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You know something.</font>

00:05:57.320 --> 00:06:02.420
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I have recalled... an old memory.</font>

00:06:06.420 --> 00:06:09.320
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">He called my name with such a gentle voice.</font>

00:06:10.500 --> 00:06:14.240
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">He gave me sweets from a foreign land.</font>

00:06:27.800 --> 00:06:29.150
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What are you talking about?</font>

00:06:29.780 --> 00:06:34.330
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I guess nobody knows what he 
looked like when he was young.</font>

00:06:35.050 --> 00:06:38.410
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I did hear he was completely 
different during his final years.</font>

00:06:39.010 --> 00:06:42.860
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">He never came to see me after I grew up,</font>

00:06:42.860 --> 00:06:45.220
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">so all I know about him is through rumors.</font>

00:06:45.940 --> 00:06:47.650
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Who do you mean?</font>

00:06:47.650 --> 00:06:49.930
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You look just like him.</font>

00:06:49.930 --> 00:06:51.300
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What are you talking about?!</font>

00:06:51.770 --> 00:06:57.620
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">He too had a voice as sweet as honey,</font>

00:06:57.620 --> 00:07:01.100
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">and a face like a beautiful goddess.</font>

00:07:02.090 --> 00:07:07.880
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Why is someone of your status 
pretending to be a eunuch?</font>

00:07:11.910 --> 00:07:13.100
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Arrest her!</font>

00:07:13.780 --> 00:07:14.970
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Let me go!</font>

00:07:14.970 --> 00:07:16.120
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Stop resisting!</font>

00:07:17.640 --> 00:07:19.800
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Master Jinshi, what should we do?</font>

00:07:22.380 --> 00:07:23.560
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Master Jinshi?!</font>

00:07:31.630 --> 00:07:33.470
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What was that?! Poison?!</font>

00:07:35.050 --> 00:07:36.090
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Bring water!</font>

00:07:36.090 --> 00:07:36.810
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yes!</font>

00:07:38.220 --> 00:07:40.180
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Master Jinshi, your instructions!</font>

00:07:42.690 --> 00:07:43.600
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Master Jinshi!</font>

00:07:48.600 --> 00:07:52.780
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Take this woman to the doctor's office. 
Make sure she doesn't do that again!</font>

00:07:52.780 --> 00:07:53.520
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yes, sir!</font>

00:07:56.970 --> 00:07:58.650
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Please snap out of it!</font>

00:07:58.650 --> 00:08:01.240
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Don't let some servant's 
casual insult shake you!</font>

00:08:02.600 --> 00:08:03.920
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Casual?</font>

00:08:05.090 --> 00:08:07.530
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">She drank poison. 
It seems more serious than that.</font>

00:08:10.760 --> 00:08:14.510
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">She went pale when she saw me smile at her.</font>

00:08:15.040 --> 00:08:16.760
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">He too...</font>

00:08:18.200 --> 00:08:22.230
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Gaoshun, do I look like him?</font>

00:08:22.670 --> 00:08:25.780
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Enough to make someone 
drink poison out of fear?</font>

00:08:28.050 --> 00:08:32.810
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">In my memory, he was 
already a withered old man.</font>

00:08:34.940 --> 00:08:38.120
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I didn't look like my mother or my brother.</font>

00:08:38.930 --> 00:08:39.760
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">So...</font>

00:08:40.930 --> 00:08:42.460
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">So, I believed.</font>

00:08:43.950 --> 00:08:46.250
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I wonder where he got his looks from?</font>

00:08:46.250 --> 00:08:51.140
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Given the emperor's tastes, it couldn't 
be the empress, not at her age.</font>

00:08:53.000 --> 00:08:56.660
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">That's why everyone's saying 
he's an illegitimate child.</font>

00:09:04.350 --> 00:09:07.510
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>I believed the rumors that said 
I had no connection to him.</i></font>

00:09:07.950 --> 00:09:10.520
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>I tried to escape the position of crown prince.</i></font>

00:09:11.570 --> 00:09:14.280
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>I begged my brother, the emperor, 
to let me take on a eunuch's identity,</i></font>

00:09:14.280 --> 00:09:18.350
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>and plant myself in the garden
 of women. All for what?</i></font>

00:09:19.990 --> 00:09:21.880
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>How ridiculous.</i></font>

00:09:51.610 --> 00:09:54.440
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">But I can only do...</font>

00:09:55.230 --> 00:09:56.630
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">...what I can do.</font>

00:09:58.360 --> 00:09:59.760
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Right.</i></font>

00:09:59.760 --> 00:10:01.580
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>I can laugh at myself later.</i></font>

00:10:01.980 --> 00:10:03.710
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>For now, I have things to do.</i></font>

00:10:05.270 --> 00:10:08.790
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">That woman was paying her 
respects to this grave, correct?</font>

00:10:08.790 --> 00:10:09.560
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yes.</font>

00:10:11.970 --> 00:10:14.630
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Lantern plant? This isn't in season.</font>

00:10:16.680 --> 00:10:18.190
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Taihou...</font>

00:10:18.830 --> 00:10:21.060
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The name of a court lady 
who passed away last year.</font>

00:10:21.850 --> 00:10:26.230
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yes. She used to gather women 
around to tell ghost stories.</font>

00:10:27.730 --> 00:10:30.700
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">She was the lady-in-waiting 
to one of the concubines.</font>

00:10:37.960 --> 00:10:39.310
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Her relatives were...</i></font>

00:10:43.490 --> 00:10:46.240
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Only one person is related to Taihou by blood.</i></font>

00:10:46.780 --> 00:10:48.370
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>During the late emperor's reign,</i></font>

00:10:48.370 --> 00:10:50.990
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>she gave birth to a daughter
 after an affair with a doctor.</i></font>

00:10:53.690 --> 00:10:56.070
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>If that daughter is still alive...</i></font>

00:11:02.290 --> 00:11:03.560
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Where are you going?</font>

00:11:03.560 --> 00:11:04.670
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The Garnet Pavilion.</font>

00:11:13.890 --> 00:11:17.770
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>The concubine that Taihou served 
was later given to Shishou.</i></font>

00:11:17.770 --> 00:11:19.100
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>She gave birth to a daughter.</i></font>

00:11:19.790 --> 00:11:21.950
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>That daughter is Concubine Loulan.</i></font>

00:11:22.610 --> 00:11:26.810
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>As for the daughter of Taihou and the doctor,</i></font>

00:11:27.790 --> 00:11:30.540
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>there's no record of what happened
 to either her or the doctor,</i></font>

00:11:31.200 --> 00:11:33.100
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>who was ousted from the rear palace.</i></font>

00:11:42.980 --> 00:11:47.880
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Perhaps Concubine Loulan knows where 
the doctor and the daughter went.</i></font>

00:11:49.640 --> 00:11:54.340
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>It's just a hunch. There's no way 
to know if there's even a connection.</i></font>

00:11:55.050 --> 00:11:56.060
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>But, still...</i></font>

00:11:58.510 --> 00:11:59.360
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Please.</font>

00:12:00.670 --> 00:12:04.170
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>I will do everything I can.</i></font>

00:12:10.450 --> 00:12:12.810
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">My apologies for the sudden visit.</font>

00:12:16.840 --> 00:12:19.300
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">She says she doesn't mind.</font>

00:12:19.890 --> 00:12:21.360
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Thank you.</font>

00:12:22.690 --> 00:12:25.290
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>How strange, as always.</i></font>

00:12:25.290 --> 00:12:29.560
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Flashy outfits and matching makeup with 
sharp points at the corners of their eyes...</i></font>

00:12:30.870 --> 00:12:32.560
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>It makes them look like foxes.</i></font>

00:12:33.660 --> 00:12:36.690
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I had a question for you—</font>

00:12:40.200 --> 00:12:40.940
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Master Jinshi?</font>

00:12:43.480 --> 00:12:44.360
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What are you doing?!</font>

00:12:47.730 --> 00:12:50.330
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You used to have seven ladies-in-waiting.</font>

00:12:50.820 --> 00:12:52.590
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Where did the last one go?</font>

00:12:54.020 --> 00:12:58.950
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I keep track of the faces and names of all 
of the ladies-in-waiting working here.</font>

00:12:59.870 --> 00:13:03.820
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Your group changes outfits 
and makeup almost every day,</font>

00:13:04.340 --> 00:13:07.390
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">so I made note of features 
that were easy to track.</font>

00:13:07.710 --> 00:13:11.910
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">For example, the shapes of your lips or eyes,</font>

00:13:12.820 --> 00:13:14.250
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">and also...</font>

00:13:16.200 --> 00:13:17.740
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The positions of your moles.</font>

00:13:19.380 --> 00:13:22.860
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Sourin... no, Renpu, was it?</font>

00:13:23.430 --> 00:13:24.810
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">That's your name.</font>

00:13:27.750 --> 00:13:30.040
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">This was planned all along, wasn't it?</font>

00:13:30.670 --> 00:13:32.940
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Bringing in a huge number of servants,</font>

00:13:32.940 --> 00:13:35.540
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">selecting similar-looking women to serve her...</font>

00:13:35.990 --> 00:13:39.350
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The strange outfits and makeup.</font>

00:13:39.990 --> 00:13:42.590
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">All for this.</font>

00:13:43.610 --> 00:13:44.500
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">M-Master Jinshi—</font>

00:13:44.500 --> 00:13:45.130
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Speak!</font>

00:13:45.860 --> 00:13:47.990
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Where is she?</font>

00:13:50.580 --> 00:13:52.460
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Where did she go?</font>

00:13:56.350 --> 00:13:58.310
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Where did Concubine Loulan go?!</font>

00:13:59.190 --> 00:14:01.060
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Please forgive her!</font>

00:14:01.330 --> 00:14:04.320
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Renpu really doesn't know anything.</font>

00:14:05.720 --> 00:14:08.940
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Please, forgive her...</font>

00:14:17.990 --> 00:14:20.410
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Damn it. Calm down.</i></font>

00:14:23.580 --> 00:14:26.550
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">So, she didn't tell you where she was going?</font>

00:14:27.080 --> 00:14:29.980
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">No. Only that she wouldn't be returning.</font>

00:14:30.580 --> 00:14:34.780
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">A high-ranking concubine left 
the rear palace of her own free will.</font>

00:14:50.290 --> 00:14:52.720
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>There's no value in 
continuing to question them.</i></font>

00:14:56.660 --> 00:14:58.650
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">We have every available person on the search,</font>

00:14:58.650 --> 00:15:01.130
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">but are unable to locate Concubine Loulan.</font>

00:15:01.950 --> 00:15:04.260
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">There's no need to call her 
"Concubine" anymore.</font>

00:15:05.950 --> 00:15:08.380
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Leaving the rear palace 
is a serious crime.</font>

00:15:08.780 --> 00:15:10.940
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Especially for a high-ranking concubine.</font>

00:15:12.310 --> 00:15:14.640
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">She must have planned this knowing that.</font>

00:15:15.050 --> 00:15:16.000
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yes...</font>

00:15:17.190 --> 00:15:20.440
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Bringing the daughter of a high-ranking 
official into the rear palace</i></font>

00:15:20.780 --> 00:15:23.060
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>is a deal that benefits the emperor, as well.</i></font>

00:15:23.910 --> 00:15:28.540
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>He can trap them in the birdcage 
that is the rear palace as a hostage.</i></font>

00:15:30.020 --> 00:15:33.780
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Shishou seemed to care for his daughter a lot.</i></font>

00:15:34.140 --> 00:15:37.310
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>But who knows how he really felt?</i></font>

00:15:40.530 --> 00:15:43.170
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>I wonder how it was for Maomao.</i></font>

00:15:44.250 --> 00:15:47.980
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>She said one time that it's like 
a courtesan trying to quit.</i></font>

00:15:49.490 --> 00:15:51.530
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Did she go with them willingly?</i></font>

00:15:52.230 --> 00:15:55.300
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>No, if she had, she wouldn't 
have left a note like that.</i></font>

00:15:56.260 --> 00:15:59.390
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Where did she go, and why?</i></font>

00:16:05.340 --> 00:16:06.520
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What?</font>

00:16:06.900 --> 00:16:08.720
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Maomao is...</font>

00:16:08.720 --> 00:16:10.650
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">missing...?</font>

00:16:16.590 --> 00:16:19.450
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Wait for me, Maomao!</font>

00:16:20.370 --> 00:16:24.900
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Papa's coming to rescue you!</font>

00:16:27.100 --> 00:16:29.750
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Master Lakan!</font>

00:16:31.390 --> 00:16:33.300
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">How did he find out?</font>

00:16:33.300 --> 00:16:35.760
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">It seems to have leaked out somehow.</font>

00:16:38.090 --> 00:16:41.610
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Also, Shishou is currently missing.</font>

00:16:42.440 --> 00:16:44.850
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Was he colluding with Loulan?</font>

00:16:45.150 --> 00:16:50.140
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I don't know. But he is the father 
of an escaped concubine.</font>

00:16:50.140 --> 00:16:53.900
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">He will be charged with
 crimes against the emperor.</font>

00:16:54.790 --> 00:16:56.490
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I understand.</font>

00:16:57.050 --> 00:17:00.580
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Oh, and, regarding the court lady 
from yesterday... Shenlü.</font>

00:17:01.160 --> 00:17:03.070
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">She's no longer in mortal danger.</font>

00:17:04.360 --> 00:17:05.390
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Is she awake?</font>

00:17:06.110 --> 00:17:07.670
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">No, not yet.</font>

00:17:09.220 --> 00:17:13.280
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">However, we've confirmed that 
she had connections to Taihou.</font>

00:17:13.870 --> 00:17:16.730
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">That's probably why she 
participated in this rebellion.</font>

00:17:17.660 --> 00:17:19.350
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Is everyone in the clinic part of this?</font>

00:17:20.220 --> 00:17:21.140
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">No,</font>

00:17:22.380 --> 00:17:26.260
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">none of the others knew about it.</font>

00:17:29.710 --> 00:17:35.110
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Yet they helped her, probably because 
they all shared the resentment Shenlü held.</i></font>

00:17:36.360 --> 00:17:38.300
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>With the late emperor gone,</i></font>

00:17:38.300 --> 00:17:42.490
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>their anger is directed 
toward the rear palace itself.</i></font>

00:17:46.450 --> 00:17:51.160
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>I must find Loulan immediately, 
but there's just not enough information.</i></font>

00:17:51.650 --> 00:17:53.820
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Should I go after Shishou first?</i></font>

00:17:54.920 --> 00:17:57.800
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>No, someone else is doing that already.</i></font>

00:18:03.870 --> 00:18:04.970
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Who could that be?</font>

00:18:05.780 --> 00:18:06.390
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Enter.</font>

00:18:08.330 --> 00:18:09.940
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Excuse me.</font>

00:18:20.690 --> 00:18:21.950
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>An abacus?</i></font>

00:18:22.460 --> 00:18:23.520
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What do you want?</font>

00:18:26.140 --> 00:18:28.360
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">It's a pleasure to make your acquaintance.</font>

00:18:28.360 --> 00:18:30.500
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">My name is Kan Lahan.</font>

00:18:31.880 --> 00:18:37.300
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>There are only two people with the "La" 
name in the outer court: Lakan and Lahan.</i></font>

00:18:37.970 --> 00:18:40.960
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>It's a courtesy name, historically 
given by the imperial family.</i></font>

00:18:42.420 --> 00:18:46.070
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">A member of the La family. 
You must be the strategist's adopted son.</font>

00:18:46.070 --> 00:18:47.160
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What do you want?</font>

00:18:48.440 --> 00:18:50.980
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I wanted to show you this.</font>

00:18:59.000 --> 00:19:00.080
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">This is...</font>

00:19:00.680 --> 00:19:02.240
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What do you think?</font>

00:19:03.720 --> 00:19:05.660
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">A receipt journal for 
the national treasury.</font>

00:19:06.080 --> 00:19:10.280
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yes. My father told me to look into it.</font>

00:19:10.280 --> 00:19:14.350
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">It didn't sit well with him that we 
can't find where the feifa came from.</font>

00:19:14.760 --> 00:19:16.460
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">How did that lead to the national treasury?</font>

00:19:16.910 --> 00:19:21.820
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">It was natural, after investigating the
 situations of recently punished officials.</font>

00:19:22.600 --> 00:19:28.160
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I wanted you to see the original 
documents, but they got a bit lengthy.</font>

00:19:28.890 --> 00:19:31.630
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">So I made an excerpt based 
on the most obvious ones.</font>

00:19:32.860 --> 00:19:37.190
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The price of grain has gone up 
visibly over the past few years.</font>

00:19:37.190 --> 00:19:39.160
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Interesting, isn't it?</font>

00:19:39.160 --> 00:19:41.930
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">We've had no droughts 
nor insect plagues, nothing like that.</font>

00:19:42.440 --> 00:19:46.660
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">And one more thing: for some reason, 
the price of iron has increased, as well.</font>

00:19:47.310 --> 00:19:49.990
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">As have the prices of all metals nationwide.</font>

00:19:52.270 --> 00:19:56.430
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Is our government building 
some huge structure somewhere?</font>

00:19:56.850 --> 00:20:01.260
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I couldn't find any plans for such a
project anywhere that I looked.</font>

00:20:01.900 --> 00:20:05.040
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>He's just like his adopted father 
in that cunning, shrewd way.</i></font>

00:20:06.120 --> 00:20:07.760
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I understand what you're trying to say.</font>

00:20:08.300 --> 00:20:11.050
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The price of grain
isn't extraordinary by itself,</font>

00:20:11.050 --> 00:20:15.830
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">but given the volume of trade, that small 
price hike results in a huge difference.</font>

00:20:16.510 --> 00:20:19.530
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Someone is pocketing that difference.</font>

00:20:20.100 --> 00:20:25.510
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Also, the price of metals means 
someone is buying a lot of them.</font>

00:20:26.460 --> 00:20:28.030
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">That's what you're implying, right?</font>

00:20:28.540 --> 00:20:34.380
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yes. From what I'm thinking, 
these both lead to the same thing.</font>

00:20:34.380 --> 00:20:39.200
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">And there aren't very many people 
who can pull off something like this.</font>

00:20:41.660 --> 00:20:45.760
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I could look into it in more detail.</font>

00:20:47.100 --> 00:20:52.510
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Wouldn't it interest you to know 
where all this is flowing?</font>

00:21:00.100 --> 00:21:02.070
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">And what do you want in return?</font>

00:21:04.550 --> 00:21:07.850
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You couldn't have brought this to me 
without asking for something in return.</font>

00:21:07.850 --> 00:21:08.740
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Master Jinshi!</font>

00:21:10.880 --> 00:21:17.020
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Could you give us just 
a <i>small</i> discount on this bill?</font>

00:21:17.020 --> 00:21:17.830
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What's that for?</font>

00:21:18.110 --> 00:21:22.270
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">It's the cost of repairs for the gate into 
the rear palace that my father destroyed.</font>

00:21:23.460 --> 00:21:25.630
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">He should reap what he sows...</font>

00:21:26.010 --> 00:21:26.930
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Fine.</font>

00:21:26.930 --> 00:21:28.390
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Are you sure?!</font>

00:21:31.110 --> 00:21:33.840
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">In exchange, I expect you to be thorough.</font>

00:21:33.840 --> 00:21:38.340
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Find out what's going on at the destination
 of this trail of money and metal.</font>

00:21:42.710 --> 00:21:44.650
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">As you wish.</font>

00:21:46.650 --> 00:21:50.110
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>I'll use whatever I can.</i></font>

00:23:45.060 --> 00:24:00.000
<font face="Times New Roman" size="22">{\an7}Next Time</font>

00:23:56.660 --> 00:23:59.220
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>{\an8}Next time: "Festival."</i></font>

00:23:56.740 --> 00:24:00.000
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20">{\an3}Episode 43: Festival</font>

